00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Hi there, here's my Lipo 6 review, a product I'd 
 heard of and wanted to find out more about

00:00:10.634 --> 00:00:21.634
The official description of LIPO-6 by Nutrex is that it’s 
“a powerful and extremely popular 
 fat-burner that utilizes maximum strength liquid capsules for superior absorption and rapid results. “

00:00:22.862 --> 00:00:27.862
Apparently it was even awarded the title of Fat-Loss Product 
 of the Year for 3 straight years running.

00:00:28.010 --> 00:00:30.010
Pretty Impressive!

00:00:30.010 --> 00:00:32.010
This is what they say about Lipo 6 for men:

00:00:33.706 --> 00:00:39.706
The highly advanced liquid capsule formula of LIPO-6 causes 
 a strong overall fat-burning effect in men. 

00:00:40.487 --> 00:00:46.487
When men begin to lose body fat they rapidly notice 
 enhanced muscle definition and a leaner midsection. 

00:00:47.016 --> 00:00:51.016
With a reduction in body fat love handles and lower 
 back fat deposits begin to disappear as well. 

00:00:57.863 --> 00:00:59.863
This is what they say about Lipo 6 for women:

00:01:01.489 --> 00:01:06.489
LIPO-6 Liquid Capsule is scientifically engineered to be successfully used by women.

00:01:07.624 --> 00:01:14.624
Besides igniting a strong thermogenic effect that leads to 
 a rapid loss of overall body fat, 

00:01:16.890 --> 00:01:20.890
LIPO-6 also assists in controlling your appetite. 

00:01:21.726 --> 00:01:27.726
On first glance it looks like a pretty solid product that’s been around 
 for a while and works to help you lose some weight.

00:01:28.098 --> 00:01:31.098
So just like you I went around looking for reviews on it. – 

00:01:32.499 --> 00:01:39.499
I actually found a ton of reviews on various sites across the internet, 
 mostly positive but there were a few negative reviews I found too.

00:01:40.916 --> 00:01:43.920
One person even said “they were as effective as M&amp;amp;Ms”

00:01:44.653 --> 00:01:51.650
I guess you’ll get that with any product though, and the good reviews 
 far far out weigh the bad which is the most important thing.

00:01:52.376 --> 00:02:02.380
There’s some great before and after pictures on this site, and you can find a ton more 
 reviews and testimonials by clicking the link underneath this video and clicking on the Testimonials tab.

00:02:03.458 --> 00:02:09.460
One thing that kept cropping up on a lot of the reviews I found 
 is that it’s really important to follow the directions on the packet.

00:02:10.750 --> 00:02:21.750
And also, that just using the pills on their own won’t cause you to lose weight – you do have 
 to eat sensibly and exercise at the same time so your weight loss should be a three pronged approach.

00:02:22.709 --> 00:02:27.710
Most people recommend 5-6 smaller meals a day, rather than 3 large meals.

00:02:28.784 --> 00:02:34.780
So overall, it seems that a lot of people are really loving 
 Lipo 6 and the weight loss results they’re achieving with it.

